title: S1, E2: Messy As F**k
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary: Love is messy. And so is dating. Crissle and Fran share some personal dating experiences that are funnily enough very similar to Molly’s. Listen in to see who’s about that #applife and who’s not, in this week’s deep dive of HBO’s Insecure.
